<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 02:38:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普停火延期后，伊朗加大对霍尔木兹海峡船只的攻击力度（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension</link><description>&lt;p&gt;由于伊朗拒绝承诺进行和谈，停火的未来仍然存在疑问。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension"&gt;特朗普停火延期后伊朗加大对霍尔木兹海峡船只的攻击力度（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:07:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-ramps-up-attacks-on-ships-in-the-strait-of-hormuz-after-trump-ceasefire-extension</guid></item><item><title>我们刚刚了解到的有关特朗普级战列舰计划的所有新消息</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/everything-new-we-just-learned-about-the-trump-class-battleship-program</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我们正在更清楚地了解海军如何使用这些舰艇，每艘舰艇的估计成本为 17B 美元。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/everything-new-we-just-learned-about-the-trump-class-battleship-program"&gt;我们刚刚了解到的有关特朗普级战列舰计划的一切新消息&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 23:25:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/everything-new-we-just-learned-about-the-trump-class-battleship-program</guid></item><item><title>新型低成本巡航导弹具有类似战斧的射程</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/new-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-features-tomahawk-like-range</link><description>&lt;p&gt;RAACM-ER 巡航导弹的射程超过 1,000 海里，旨在以更低的成本射程更远。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/new-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-features-tomahawk-like-range"&gt;具有类似战斧射程的新型低成本巡航导弹&lt;/a&gt;后首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 20:16:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/new-raacm-er-low-cost-cruise-missile-features-tomahawk-like-range</guid></item><item><title>美国海军 MH-60S 飞行员在海鹰巡演期间谈论多任务角色</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/u-s-navy-mh-60s-pilot-talks-multi-mission-roles-during-tour-of-the-seahawk</link><description>&lt;p&gt;品牌内容：MH-60S 是真正的美国海军主力，从执行舰艇补给到扫雷再到反水面战。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/u-s-navy-mh-60s-pilot-talks-multi-mission-roles-during-tour-of-the-seahawk"&gt;美国海军 MH-60S 飞行员在海鹰巡演期间谈论多任务角色&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 19:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/u-s-navy-mh-60s-pilot-talks-multi-mission-roles-during-tour-of-the-seahawk</guid></item><item><title>美国空军的 F-15EX 购买量刚刚增加一倍，这非常有意义</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-buy-was-just-doubled-by-the-usaf-which-makes-perfect-sense</link><description>&lt;p&gt;虽然它最初是取代 F-15C，但更多的 F-15EX 将为老化的 F-15E 攻击鹰和可能的其他类型提供现成的继任者。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-buy-was-just-doubled-by-the-usaf-which-makes-perfect-sense"&gt;美国空军将 F-15EX 的购买量增加了一倍，这非常有意义，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 18:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/f-15ex-buy-was-just-doubled-by-the-usaf-which-makes-perfect-sense</guid></item><item><title>福特级审查使海军未来的航母计划受到质疑</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/ford-class-review-puts-navys-future-carrier-plans-into-question</link><description>&lt;p&gt;审查包括将福特级与尼米兹级进行比较，并了解操作上的收获或损失。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/ford-class-review-puts-navys-future-carrier-plans-into-question"&gt;福特级评论后对海军未来航母计划提出质疑&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 17:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/ford-class-review-puts-navys-future-carrier-plans-into-question</guid></item><item><title>莱昂纳多·DRS 为美国海军对抗无人机的计划</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/leonardo-drss-plan-to-counter-drones-for-the-u-s-navy</link><description>&lt;p&gt;品牌内容：海上任务装备包 (M-MEP) 旨在保护海上资产免受攻击无人机的攻击。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/leonardo-drss-plan-to-counter-drones-for-the-u-s-navy"&gt;莱昂纳多·DRS 的美国海军反无人机计划&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 15:36:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sponsored-content/leonardo-drss-plan-to-counter-drones-for-the-u-s-navy</guid></item><item><title>特朗普延长停火期限（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-seizes-first-iranian-linked-ship-outside-the-middle-east-region-since-epic-fury-began</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在印度洋拦截 M/T Tifani 号油轮标志着针对伊朗经济战的新策略，而几天前就已经预示了这一策略。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-seizes-first-iranian-linked-ship-outside-the-middle-east-region-since-epic-fury-began"&gt;特朗普延长停火期限（更新）&lt;/a&gt;的帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-seizes-first-iranian-linked-ship-outside-the-middle-east-region-since-epic-fury-began</guid></item><item><title>斯普鲁恩斯号航空母舰用甲板炮炸毁一艘船是近四年来的第一次</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/uss-spruance-blasting-a-ship-with-its-deck-gun-is-a-first-in-nearly-four-decades</link><description>&lt;p&gt;自 1988 年以来，海军还没有在愤怒中用甲板炮击中过另一艘船。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/uss-spruance-blasting-a-ship-with-its-deck-gun-is-a-first-in-nearly-four-decades"&gt;美国海军斯普鲁恩斯号用甲板炮炸毁一艘船是近四年来的第一次，&l